{"tid":801351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普揚言退出WTO 俄羅斯：美國經濟將受創","createTime":"2018-08-31T14:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T07:12:17.000Z","uid":141151,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"679710ac5cc79fa80af05218117faff8b0421bec","tid":801351,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:23:39.000Z","msg":"川普揚言退出WTO 俄羅斯：美國經濟將受創<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4194185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4194185&d=wlg5qpysbMwI8blMwSHqzf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=83d71db9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4194185</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普揚言，若世界貿易組織 (WTO) 不改變對待美國的方式，美國將退出 WTO；對此，俄羅斯經濟部今 (31) 日表示，若此事成真，美國將蒙受經濟損失。<br />\n<br />\n川普日前接受彭博新聞專訪，他指出，建立 WTO 的協議，是「最糟糕的」貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n川普稱，美國很少在 WTO 贏得官司，但去年除外，「因為他們知道，若我們贏不了，我就會走人。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據路透社報導，俄羅斯經濟部認為，川普不照遊戲規則走，若美國退出 WTO，將使其經濟受創。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，川普經常表達，想讓美國退出 WTO 的看法；早在 6 月底，美國媒體 AXIOS 便引述不具名消息來源說法，稱川普「講了不下百次 (退出 WTO)」，只因他覺得，美國被 WTO 搞得一團亂。<br />\n</span><br />\n報導指出，部分官員向川普解釋，美國創造 WTO 體系，也建立了貿易律師團，自 1995 年以來，在 WTO 架構下贏得的案件占比，達 85.7%，不僅高於平均值 (84.4%)，表現也比中國 (66.7%) 好。<br />\n<br />\n然而，川普對上述論點，感到不以為然。"},{"pid":"ff1e1cdc1096dc5f60ba8322968a13cf80f20d37","tid":801351,"uid":55924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"咁熟既呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218f5e17a4392ba8dc31cef8fd1d56d8678406b9","tid":801351,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"好想陪佢一齊離開WTO<br />\n侵侵快啲帶我地走"},{"pid":"2e4175d1e69535e3129ffbd7565f6b51eddaf5d3","tid":801351,"uid":202698,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:31:04.000Z","msg":"侵侵鳩up啫，以為真係會退？"},{"pid":"974aeab159fb7bd0627307459ba8b2a52a5d5d80","tid":801351,"uid":115510,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2e4175d1e69535e3129ffbd7565f6b51eddaf5d3","tid":801351,"uid":202698,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:31:04.000Z","msg":"侵侵鳩up啫，以為真係會退？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"佢係狂人"},{"pid":"be40b3dbdd88b1ca79b1905b124f4f311e2e8bcb","tid":801351,"uid":2923,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"侵侵：美國同歐洲同日本組成新經濟貿易組織,睇下邊個贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243ea53c218e080718a400c425c866e616f7c338","tid":801351,"uid":23180,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"既然美國會輸，俄中應該支持佢退出"},{"pid":"6e694fc3fe7a172e0cb1524cdb0ce5125b71050f","tid":801351,"uid":30169,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"243ea53c218e080718a400c425c866e616f7c338","tid":801351,"uid":23180,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"既然美國會輸，俄中應該支持佢退出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023c71a6db856b2506720acbd15edc0e4b3771a5","tid":801351,"uid":204929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"全部民主國家 之後集體退出, 在成立一個新嘅類似wto嘅嘢"},{"pid":"1619057d2817dda96b5d50bb080d8d84d6be6dc2","tid":801351,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"講埋啲廢話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245a6417eb7d82a79baa15036faa5c3b1d98b6ae","tid":801351,"uid":27664,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:39:14.000Z","msg":"俄佬終於搵到幾會快過贏國口交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c9c0a887abadb5f9bf6b05e5427411244134e0","tid":801351,"uid":52946